data.description: Welcome to 2825 Kings Retreat in The Villas of Kingwood! This stunning home offers a spacious layout with plenty of natural light and a brand new vinyl plank flooring. The kitchen features stainless appliances, quartz counters, and a beautiful island with breakfast bar. The master bedroom boasts high ceilings, custom plantation shutters, and a luxurious en-suite with a jetted garden tub and separate shower. The secondary bedroom has its own private bathroom, and there is even a flex room that could be used as a study or 3rd bedroom. With gated access, private lakes, and proximity to dining and entertainment options, this home is a must-see. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity - schedule your private tour today!
